Project name: mini autonomous data warehouse builder

Description:
Two AI agents using openai or ollama to read, tranform and save new schema and table(s), that are then visualized and conluded

Architecture idea for ai pipeline:

1. Agent one - Data Egineer

    Input: raw files (JSON, CSV, Excel, Parquet)

    Responsibilities:
    Detect file type
    Infer schema
    Normalize data
    Create tables
    Load into database / lakehouse

    Outputs:

    structured tables
    schema description


2. Agent two - Analyst

    Input: structured tables

    Responsibilities:
    understand schema
    generate python queries
    compute metrics
    produce charts
    summarize trends

    Outputs:
    insights
    visualizations
    natural language explanations